| plan_type     | plan                                                                                                                                                                                                                  |
+---------------+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------+
| logical_plan  | Projection: vector_search(qs, Utf8("second"), answer).subject                                                                                                                                                         |
