|               |       ProjectionExec: expr=[subject@1 as subject, _score@0 as _score]                                                                                                                                                 |
|               |         HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Left, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(id@0, id@0)], projection=[_score@1, subject@3]                                                                        |
